{"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"title":"OUDSBulletList","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSBulletList","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","platforms":[{"name":"iOS","introducedAt":"15.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"name":"macOS","introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"name":"tvOS","introducedAt":"16.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"name":"visionOS","introducedAt":"1.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"name":"watchOS","introducedAt":"11.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents14OUDSBulletListV","symbolKind":"struct","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSBulletList","kind":"identifier"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Bullet list is a UI element that helps to view in related individual text items grouped together; items usually starting with a number or a bullet."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Bullet list is also known as "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Unordered list"}]},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Ordered list"}]},{"type":"text","text":" and is not an interactive element by default."}],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Structures","anchor":"Structures","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/Item"]},{"generated":true,"title":"Initializers","anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/init(type:textStyle:isBold:items:)"]},{"generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties","anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/body"]},{"generated":true,"title":"Enumerations","anchor":"Enumerations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/TextStyle","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/Type","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/UnorderedAsset"]},{"generated":true,"title":"Default Implementations","anchor":"Default-Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/View-Implementations"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList"},"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"kind":"relationships"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSBulletList","kind":"identifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/ContentDisplay"],"kind":"mentions"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Types","level":2,"text":"Types"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Three types are proposed:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Unordered (by default)"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Collects related items that don’t need to be in a specific order or sequence."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Ordered"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Collects related items with numeric order or sequence."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Bare"}]},{"type":"text","text":": An unordered list without any bullets or alphanumeric sequence."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Types can be mixed in list, but must be identical for the same "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSBulletList.NestedLevel"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Levels","anchor":"Levels"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Lists can include nested items to indicate hierarchy or subcategories, with indentation distinguishing each level."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Arrange ordered list items logically, such as ranking by importance, highest to lowest values, or in alphabetical \/ numeric order."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Three levels are maximum."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Text-Style","text":"Text Style","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"List can be used with different font sizes:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Body Large"}]},{"type":"text","text":": If the text accompanying the list component is the Body Large text. This variant is designed for more visual, engaging experiences."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Body Medium"}]},{"type":"text","text":": If the text accompanying the list component is the Body Medium text. This variant is best suited for functional, task-oriented experiences."}]}]}]},{"anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Cases forbidden by design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"it is not allowed to have a depth of items greater than 3"}],"type":"strong"}]},{"anchor":"Internationalisation-considerations","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Internationalisation considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For latin-based speaking countries, like France, Spain, United Kingdom or Belgium, the european “arabic” numbers are used for the first level of depth","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the ordered bullet list. For the second and third levels, the european alphabets are used with upper and lower case values.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"However for countries speaking arabic, these rules can’t be applied. Indeed, there is no notion of upper and lower case characters in arabic alphabet.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In addition, the numbers in use (i.e. the european “arabic” numbers like “1, 2, 3”) are accepted in arabic countries, even if the “true arabic” numbers (like “ ٢ ٣ ١”) are used","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in middle-east arabic countries and for official documents.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Thus the OUDS ordered bullet list will use “european” numbers for first level, and arabic alphabets for second and third levels.","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Code samples"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["       \/\/ 1. Unordered list with bullets","       OUDSBulletList {","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 2\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 3\")","       }","","       \/\/ 1.1. Item of Unordered list with bullet as tick, a text style","       \/\/ body medium and text bold","       OUDSBulletList(type: .unordered(asset: .tick),","                      textStyle: .bodyMedium,","                      isBold: true)  {","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 2\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 3\")","       }","","       \/\/ 2. Bare list with 3 items","       OUDSBulletList(type: .bare) {","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 2\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 3\")","       }","","       \/\/ 3. Ordered list with 3 items","       OUDSBulletList(type: .ordered) {","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 2\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 3\")","       }","","       \/\/ 3.1. Ordered list with 3 items in first level,","       \/\/ and one item as sub item (second level),","       \/\/ and 2 items as sub item in (third level)","       OUDSBulletList(type: .ordered) {","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1\") {","               OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1.1\") {","                   OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1.1.1\")","                   OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1.1.2\")","               }","           }","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 2\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 3\")","       }","","       \/\/ Same Bullet list but items in third level with free icon as bullet","       let icon = Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\")","       OUDSBulletList(type: .ordered) {","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1\") {","               OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1.1\", subListType: .unordered(asset: .icon(icon))) {","                   OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1.1.1\")","                   OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1.1.2\")","               }","           }","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 2\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 3\")","       }"]},{"anchor":"Rich-text","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Rich text"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Rich text can be applied only if ","type":"text"},{"code":"isBold","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" flag is set to ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"false"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Strong text can be used sparingly within alert messages to highlight key information.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Underlined text must not be used for emphasis, as it is commonly associated with links.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If a hyperlink is needed within the content, the underlined style should be used.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Italic should be used with care, some brands do not allow it like Orange brand.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"No other text styles should be used.","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Always check the results of rich text mode with high contrast, light and dark modes, and Voice Over vocalization.","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Design documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-bullet-list","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]},{"anchor":"Themes-rendering","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Themes rendering"},{"anchor":"Orange","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_bullet_list_Orange","type":"image"}]},{"anchor":"Orange-Compact","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Orange Compact"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_bullet_list_OrangeCompact","type":"image"}]},{"anchor":"Sosh","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_bullet_list_Sosh","type":"image"}]},{"anchor":"Wireframe","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_bullet_list_Wireframe